  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) 1,200 poor widows provided free healthcare for minor ailments.

2) 90 widows with chronic diseases given free treatment from a secondary/tertiary healthcare facility.

3) 1,200 widows linked to an accessible and affordable healthcare facility and awareness increased on health-related issues from 20% to 80% within 2 years.</narrative>
  </description>
